Scottish Premiership: What did we learn?

The Scottish Premiership is back with big wins, goals, drama and more - here is what we learned...

12/08/24 11:00am

Dundee coast to victory over Hearts to go top of fledgling table

Dundee moved to the top of the fledgling Premiership table by capitalising on a calamitous first-half display from Hearts to run out 3-1 winners at Dens Park.

10/08/24 8:05pm
